column5: Happy birthday Art.  I'll toast the occasion with a glass of wine in a bit.

Hope you have a good one. Joe
Art, Happy Birthday man!!!  G
Best Fishes to Art!!!  Hope you have a great one Bubba!!!
Happy B-Day Art and all the best to ya !!
Happy Birthday to you my friend. You have the bestest day!
Hope it's one of the bestest yet bud!
Happy Birthday Art!  May it be a good one for ya
All the best on your Birthday...
Very best wishes Art. Have a great day.
Bonne Fete, Art, and as we Acadians say, Laissez les Bon Temps Rouler!
Happy Birthday Art!!!!!  Have a super, duper day from one Taurus to another    I guess we're both full of bull  Joey
